    "content": "server/tests/test_tiff_encode.py :: test_encode_decode_roundtrip_uncompressed\ndef test_encode_decode_roundtrip_uncompressed():\n    raster = gradient_raster(24, 16)\n    encoded = encode_tiff(raster, compression=\"none\")\n    decoded = decode_tiff(encoded)\n    assert decoded.width == raster.width\n    assert decoded.height == raster.height\n    assert bytes(decoded.data) == bytes(raster.to_rgb().data)",
